      • convert

        public Optional<PostalAddressType> convert(Map<String,Object> map)
        This method creates an PostalAddressType from the values in the provided map. The following keys are expected in the provided map (Taken from EbrimConstants):

        CITY = "city"; COUNTRY = "country"; POSTAL_CODE = "postalCode"; STATE_OR_PROVINCE = "stateOrProvince"; STREET = "street"; STREET_NUMBER = "streetNumber";

        Parameters:
        map - the Map representation of the PostalAddressType to generate, null returns empty Optional
        Returns:
        Optional PostalAddressType created from the values in the map
